articles.title: Joey Chestnut reclaims title in Nathan's Famous hot dog eating contest, wins 17th Mustard Belt - AP News
articles.description: Famed competitive eater Joey “Jaws” Chestnut has reclaimed his title at the Nathan’s Famous Fourth of July hot dog eating contest after skipping last year’s event. The 41-year-old from Westfield, Indiana, secured his 17th Mustard Belt in 20 appearances before…
